# VERSION CONTROL
# -----------------------------------------------
.git/
.gitignore
.github/

# -----------------------------------------------
# DOCUMENTATION
# -----------------------------------------------
*.md
README*
CHANGELOG*
LICENSE*
docs/
documentation/

